{"tid":1825971,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"教貓分享","createTime":"2020-01-15T18:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:22:44.000Z","uid":313312,"like":5,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e8104e1ffa4024cf08b92c232dca42a6f0118a3a","tid":1825971,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:10:14.000Z","msg":"分享我朋友教貓心得，覺得唔錯<br />\n<br />\n首先貓冇狗既同人類相處天性，由歷史睇人訓練狗歷史更長，但唔代表貓唔識聽指令。<br />\n<br />\n天下間所有動物都會對痛產生記憶，所以教大家痛楚記憶法，例如當隻貓做你唔鐘意既事情，例如爬高，就要捉黎打，打都要有指標，唔可以往死裏打，咁要打到咩程度先叫夠先可以停？只要隻貓打到失禁咁就代表達標，當然想效果更好可以打多幾下，如果驚打傷隻貓，可以去街市買藤條，你話驚俾屋企人知，可以用水刑，開桶水，或直接用花灑。<br />\n<br />\n當然痛楚記憶法越細訓練越好，從細開始俾貓知道誰係大佬，唔好俾貓劃地盤，俾佢認為佢係生活你既地盤。要俾貓對主人有敬畏。<br />\n<br />\n要細個開始用手指伸入貓既嘴，迫佢習慣，佢想咬電線，就用電線打佢，用電線塞入佢嘴，塞到佢想嘔。開門如果佢跑出去，就打，打完再開門，一行近門口又打，自然佢就唔會行近門口<br />\n<br />\n發情處理，一發情就幫佢沖凍水涼，一沖完就安靜，真係萬試萬靈<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好用索帶，朋友之前用索打，失左手，不過好彩幾個月貨仔，哂幾千<br />\n<br />\n以上就係我朋友教貓經驗，有咩想問，我可以轉介<br />\n<br />\n貓係畜生，係玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159bbbc9e032ff5b1a1d175726020378242c966c","tid":1825971,"uid":84594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:13:05.000Z","msg":"乜撚野呀"},{"pid":"7c1f733c4e25434fc571b8d7e1b1b4a364c535fb","tid":1825971,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"痴線？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手和你推<br />\n返出去推行動Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 月19 日 3 點 遮打道見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFBuTnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFBuTnf.jpg&h=38f39617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3:00 pm 遮打道 見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cbdf2eda4d32fad9ce5e113b425f9ec18f117ef7","tid":1825971,"uid":313312,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:15:53.000Z","msg":"有時睇見人地既貓好無家教真係好想摙死佢<br />\n<br />\n明明我朋友隻貓由細到大都未咬或抓過人，連客氣無，抱一個鐘都唔會反抗，點解其他人可以縱容隻貓咬人，就算玩都接受唔到，或者到處去廁所，真係好無家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8738bceaf4b1102133490ff7b1ba88002d8e9eb5","tid":1825971,"uid":313312,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:20:20.000Z","msg":"點解貓，仲未去到狗咁既水準，就係班貓奴唔撚識教拖慢哂貓適應力"},{"pid":"99969124040792c0454503d2794f7299db1c98fa","tid":1825971,"uid":114062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"我睇緊咩"},{"